    fm:responsibility "Business engagement (non-FS)"@en,
        "Departmental minister for HM Treasury Group (including responsibility for the Darlington campus)"@en,
        "Economic and business regulation and competition"@en,
        "Industrial Strategy and Trade: leading on the Treasury’s input to the industrial strategy, trade strategy and EU opportunities"@en,
        "Innovation: including leading on the Treasury’s input to R&D, AI, digital economy and diffusion"@en,
        "Leading on procurement and commercial strategy, including improving the efficiency and effectiveness of procurement"@en,
        "Leading on the Treasury’s interest in inward and foreign direct investment (non-FS)"@en,
        "Leading on the Treasury’s interest in welfare policy"@en,
        "Net Zero: leading on the Treasury’s input to the clean energy mission, including Great British Energy, decarbonisation, and green industries"@en,
        "People: leading on the Treasury’s input to skills and workforce policy, including labour market, skills and migration"@en,
        "Place: leading on the Treasury’s input to regional growth, including cities and devolution and growth elements of housing and planning"@en,
        "Supporting the Chancellor on economic security and resilience"@en,
        "Supporting the Chancellor on reforms to the UK’s Public Financial Institutions, including driving growth via the National Wealth Fund and British Business Bank"@en,
        "Supporting the Chancellor on the Growth Mission, specifically:"@en,
